# Add new recipes
&fmd "data/minecraft/recipe"
RecipePath вҶҗ $"data/minecraft/recipe/_.json"

# Multiple flint and steel recipes
вҮҢвҒ…Г—64/7 вҮЎ7
В°ЛңвҠҸ В°вҠёвҠў в–Ў"" В°вӢ• +1В°вҠҸ
вүЎ(&fwa вҠ“(
    RecipePath $"flint\_and\_steel_"
  | вҷӯвҶҜвҠҷ",\"minecraft:stick\"" +1
    $$ {
    $$   "type": "minecraft:crafting\_shapeless",
    $$   "category": "equipment",
    $$   "ingredients": [
    $$     "minecraft:raw\_iron",
    $$     "minecraft:flint"_
    $$   ],
    $$   "result": {
    $$     "count": 1,
    $$     "id": "minecraft:flint\_and\_steel",
    $$     "components": {
    $$       "damage": _
    $$     }
    $$   },
    $$   "group": "flint\_and\_steel"
    $$ }
  ))

