# Composter increase
вҹңвҶ»вӮҒ вҮЎвӮҖ8
вҚҡ$"execute if block ~ ~ ~ composter[level=_] run return run setblock ~ ~ ~ composter[level=_]"
вҚңвҠЈ(в—Үв–ЎвӮӮ"execute if block ~ ~ ~ composter[level=8] run summon item ~ ~ ~ {Item:{id:bone_meal,count:1}}")
вҠӮ{"# This file is generated""playsound block.composter.fill_success block @a"}
/в—ҮвҠӮвӮғ@\n
&fwa "data/chalc/function/fill/increase.mcfunction"

